arStrings.szText: "Marzhan, I seek an audience with Captain Kharov."
Oh, is that so? And just who might you... well well! I recall you from Faith's Torch.
Sadly, an audience with Kharov isnâ€™t within my power. He found my writings not to his liking. Truth be told, he nearly had me killed over their contents.
Maybe there is a way for you to speak with him. Ha! Maybe you'll usher me back into his good graces! Yes, I can see it now!
